google_ad_height = 280;
//-->
</script>
<script type="text/javascript"
src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js">
</script></div><p><br/></ul>
<p><br/>These are just a few of my picks.   If you like them or hate them, I&#8217;d like to know by leaving a comment.   If you have other suggestions, please feel free to leave a comment also, so Others can try them out and see if they are right for them.<br/><br />
<h2 style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #ff9900;">Stay Safe</span></h3>
<p><br/><br />
<h2 style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #ff9900;">Paul Sylvester</span></h3>
